document_data.name: Jaundamicar Bleth
document_data.mainbody:
'''Jaundamicar Bleth''' was the First Lord of the city of [[Westgate]] and controlled the [[Fire Knives]] [[thieves]]' [[guild]] in that city in [[1479 DR]].
